{"root":{"data":{"id":"djlbxrpryr40","created":1782715597958,"text":"感知评测"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djlc51wkun40","created":1782716168687,"text":"核心技能"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djlc5nb8cww0","created":1782716215285,"text":"软件测试理论基础"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djlc859p07k0","created":1782716411103,"text":"测试流程与生命周期"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djlc86ot9ls0","created":1782716414193,"text":"测试用例设计方法"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djlc89nzuq80","created":1782716420674,"text":"缺陷管理流程"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djlc8ds5qd40","created":1782716429633,"text":"测试工具"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djlc6lrehuo0","created":1782716290273,"text":"传感器与数据理解"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djlc9153oo00","created":1782716480482,"text":"摄像头成像与标定原理"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djlc96zal280","created":1782716493191,"text":"超声波雷达工作原理"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djlc9fos7xs0","created":1782716512147,"text":"毫米波雷达工作原理"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djlc9r41klk0","created":1782716537014,"text":"激光雷达工作原理"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djlca5tuwy00","created":1782716569050,"text":"多传感器同步"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djlc5pysac00","created":1782716221063,"text":"感知算法基础"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djlcahghz8g0","created":1782716594364,"text":"计算机视觉原理","note":"通过传感器获取视觉信号并转换为数字矩阵，再利用深度学习与机器学习算法提取特征，从而实现从像素解析到高级语义的理解"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djld3fm4x080","created":1782718862912,"text":"核心工作流程"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djld3k4x9qw0","created":1782718872755,"text":"图像采集","note":"利用相机等传感器获取原始视觉信号（像素），并进行去噪、色彩转换和对比度增强等操作"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djld3nhppp40","created":1782718880059,"text":"特征提取","note":"算法（如卷积神经网络）从图像中提取边缘、纹理、形状等局部特征，再逐层抽象为全局特征"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djld3py6qq80","created":1782718885408,"text":"模型推理与决策","note":"借助深度学习模型对提取的特征进行分类、定位、分割或描述，完成预定任务"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djld4qo0daw0","created":1782718965334,"text":"基础任务"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djld4vd1vz40","created":1782718975555,"text":"图像分类（Image Classification）"